  "question": "Patient with Crohn on ibuprofen and pentasa complaining of 3 perianal fistulas that appeared a week ago, his abdominal symptoms are controlled with the medications, everything is normal except for the 3 perianal fistulas on labs ESR 60, what will you give the patient?",
